b1d09158-bdd8-4334-98c9-07698df3ea8d.title: Bartender
b1d09158-bdd8-4334-98c9-07698df3ea8d.text: Good morning, what would you like?

options.text: I don't really want anything thanks.

a6c9c32e-ad40-48d4-bd3a-2f37547330b1.title: Bartender
a6c9c32e-ad40-48d4-bd3a-2f37547330b1.text:
Well we have beer, or if you want some food, we have
our home made stew and meat pies.

options.text: Could I have some stew please?
I don't really want anything thanks.

274e3db7-0013-476b-a6c4-7286bbcd739f.title: Bartender
274e3db7-0013-476b-a6c4-7286bbcd739f.text: One beer coming up. Ok, that'll be two coins.

548bb391-d7bc-4a29-a810-1eac38a43f8a.title: <player>
548bb391-d7bc-4a29-a810-1eac38a43f8a.text: Oh dear. I don't seem to have enough money.

b837fec5-fa56-438c-9581-332ab36ec979.title: <player>
b837fec5-fa56-438c-9581-332ab36ec979.text: I don't really want anything thanks.

78f655aa-9a7a-491c-9b4b-b5e18cf475eb.title: <player>
78f655aa-9a7a-491c-9b4b-b5e18cf475eb.text: Could I have some stew please?

e5d91d94-1928-4d01-a8cf-4a31ef658272.title: Bartender
e5d91d94-1928-4d01-a8cf-4a31ef658272.text: A bowl of stew, that'll be 20 coins please.
